Invocation Name: my quotes
Developer Terms of Use
des:
This skill speaks of Handpicked quotes of Famous personalities depends on your emotions. To have peace and harmony in life, the quotes helps to up lift our mood from uncertain situations. 

The user can ask quotes for emotions like Stress, Sad, Anxiety, Depression, Worry , Fear, Fail, Hurt, Lost , Disappointment, Dull and Exhaust using the given below sentences. Alexa will pick 2 quotes of famous personalities depend on the emotion what you have included in the sentences

Alexa, Ask My Quotes to Over Come "Emotions",
Alexa, Ask My Quotes for "Emotions"
Alexa, Ask My Quotes to up lift mood from "Emotions"
